A hunter, Chidube Onyema, has allegedly shot and killed his girlfriend, Chinwendu, to death for allegedly cheating on him. The incident happened on Sunday evening at Umuokirie village in Owerri, the state capital. A source said the victim visited the súspect after returning from Aba, Abia State. While with Onyema, her phone rang, which she answered, but Onyema suspected that was two-timing. He asked who the caller was, and Chinwendu tried to explain, he asked to be handed the phone. Chinwendu refused, and Onyema immediately reached for his gun and shot her in the abdomen. Police spokesman Orlando Ikeokwu said the súspect had been.